task.summary: Add, Sub, Mult, Mod support added
Integer array, new setup definition pattern and variable declaration section deleted
Variable declaration type defined in translator
Setup functions deleted from halduino.py and instead given support on halduino.ino and the translator directly
Raise error in case the statements are not part of a function
Arduino Robot support started with engines support and negative numbers support
New directories distribution. Arduino Robot US, IR and Engines support
Hit and Rotate example for Complubot
Translator adds library and special setup for the robot
WIP translator refactor deleting unnecessary code
Serial print and if statement refactored
Array support refactored for more vari typess
Boolean arrays and arrays index refactored
Check last comma transformed into a function
Halduino functions addition refactored and divided into small functions
MakeFile and commands to directly upload to the board. This version supports just the UNO board. More support coming
Makefile creation on runtime getting system variables.
No IDE needed to compile and upload to the board for any board supported
Complubot's beep control supported on halduino
Melody Test added and support to melodies for Complubot
LineFollow new example without native robot library
Support for Robot Motor libraries in Complubot
Better support for and or statements
Print Hello World test and sleep test
